Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Esquina Community School in the Municipality of Baybay, Province of Leyte, to President Carlos P. Garcia Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 780
An Act Changing the Name of the Esquina Community School in the Municipality of Baybay, Province of Leyte, to President Carlos P. Garcia Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Esquina Community School in the Municipality of Baybay, Province of Leyte, is changed to President Carlos P. Garcia Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
